    </lg>
    <lg type="stanza" n="32">
     <l n="79">12 The Fox Jumps over the Parson 's Gate</l>
    </lg>
    <lg type="stanza" n="33">
     <l n="80">13 Come Lasses and Lads</l>
    </lg>
    <lg type="stanza" n="34">
     <l n="81">14 Ride a Cock Horse to Banbury</l>
     <l n="82">Cross , &amp; c .</l>
    </lg>
    <lg type="stanza" n="35">
     <l n="83">15 Mrs. Mary Blaize</l>
    </lg>
    <lg type="stanza" n="36">
     <l n="84">16 The Great Panjandrum Himself</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
   <p>The above selections are also issued in Four Volumes , square crown 4to , attractive binding . Each containing four different books , with their Coloured Pictures and innumerable Outline Sketches .</p>
